  "description": "<h2 id=\"introduction\">Introduction</h2>\n<p>A scenic route in the Mother Canyon.</p>\n<p>This route follows the same approach as Slingshot and Manzanita.</p>\n<p>The big rappel is frequently buzzed by tourist helicopters,\nespecially during the morning and afternoon hours.</p>\n<p>Bonus points for the Chopper shot!</p>\n<h2 id=\"approach\">Approach</h2>\n<p>Starts @ Boynton Canyon TH.</p>\n<p>Follows Same Approach Canyon as <em>Slingshot</em>.</p>\n<p>Continue along sandstone ridge heading west and passing the drainage\nfor <em>Manzanita</em>.</p>\n<p>Enter the canyon directly east of R1 via an easy downclimb.</p>\n<p>Please respect all dwelling cites in this sacred area.</p>\n<h2 id=\"descent\">Descent</h2>\n<p><strong>R1</strong>: 20’ set back off tree. (This can also be\ndownclimbed RDC)</p>\n<p><strong>R2</strong>: 190' from Boulder in watercourse. Possible\nHikers Below!</p>\n<p>Continue following the watercourse for a short distance until it\nopens back up to slickrock. Before R3, don't forget to look back over\nyour left shoulder at what the chopper was checking out.</p>\n<p><strong>R3</strong>: 40' off a single bolt located on sloped wall\nLDC.</p>\n<p><strong>R4</strong>: 170' off tree next to watercourse.</p>\n<p>Walk the cougar ledge RDC at R4! Great views / photo opp of last rap\nfrom the ledge. </p>\n<h2 id=\"exit\">Exit</h2>\n<p>Stay in drainage heading left / southeast until joining with main\nboynton trail.</p>\n<h2 id=\"red_tape\">Red tape</h2>\n<h2 id=\"trip_reports_and_media\">Trip reports and media</h2>\n<p>Jerry AZ video:</p>\n<p><a\nhref=\"https://youtu.be/EuBu0sOSmQI\">https://youtu.be/EuBu0sOSmQI</a></p>\n<p><a\nhref=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CS55q1QLWgH/?utm_medium=copy_link\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CS55q1QLWgH/?utm_medium=copy_link</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"background\">Background</h2>\n<p>First Descent on Aug 21, 2020</p>\n<p>Eric Moorcroft, Paul Hallinan, Michael Skeer</p>\n<p>Route finished and updated July 30, 2021</p>\n<p>Nick Clegg, Eric Moorcroft, Kevin Iosue, Brandon Levander</p>\n<h2 id=\"beta_sites\">Beta sites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"rwl_en.png\" title=\"rwl_en.png\" alt=\"rwl_en.png\" /><a\nhref=\"https://sedonacanyoneering.com/chopper-drop/\">sedonacanyoneering.com</a>\n: Chopper Drop</li>\n<li><img src=\"rwl_en.png\" title=\"rwl_en.png\" alt=\"rwl_en.png\" /><a\nhref=\"https://wildpathsaz.com/chopper-drop-canyon/\">wildpathsaz.com</a>\n: Chopper Drop</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"trip_reports_and_media_1\">Trip reports and media</h2>\n<h2 id=\"background_1\">Background</h2>\n",
